data.description:
This recently updated end-unit is across the street from the park, tennis courts, the lake, clubhouse, and pool. Prime location to enjoy all the amenities! And being an end unit means you only share one wall and have more natural light throughout the house! Save money with the Ecobee3 Smart Thermostat - 3 room sensors and programmable comfort settings for the perfect temperature throughout the house. Hardwood and tile throughout...no carpet! We are animal lovers and know they are part of your family, so please bring your house-trained pets! The pet fee is $300 for one or $500 for two and they must be registered and current on all shots. No more than two pets. Move-in costs are first, last, and one-month security, any applicable pet fees, and $50 per applicant for background check and credit report. All occupants 18 and over must be disclosed on the application. Occupants must be approved by the homeowner's association renter's committee at an in-person meeting held the 1st and 3rd Monday of each month. You must apply by Wednesday, February 5th to move in February 15th.

Owner pays pest control, homeowner's association fees, trash pickup. Tenant pays water, electricity, cable/internet, water/sewer
